text: Dündar is a Turkish given name for males. People named Dündar include: * Dündar Aliosman, heir of Bayezid Osman and future 45th Head of the Imperial House of Osman * Dündar Kılıç (1935–1999), infamous mob boss and legendary figure in the Turkish underworld * Dündar Taşer (1925–1972), leading figure in Turkish nationalism * Dündar Gazi (1210-1298), uncle of Osman I. * Dündar Bey (death 1324) an Anatolian bey in post Seljuk era * Can Dündar (1961-), Turkish journalist Category:Turkish masculine given names
title: Dündar
